  <brief_title>Randomized Trial on the Effect of Topical Phenytoin on Healing After Fistulotomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial on the Effect of Topical Phenytoin 2% on Wound Healing After Fistulotomy</official_title>
